summary: The module supplies example Feast feature repository configurations employed in tests and documentation. It defines entities, feature views, on‑demand feature views (including pandas‑based transformations), push sources, feature services, and project‑specific settings with tags, illustrating various Feast concepts.
business_intent: Offer ready‑made sample repositories that demonstrate how to set up and use Feast components, enabling developers to test, demo, and learn Feast functionality without creating repositories from scratch.
